# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# GLOBAL IGNORES (applies to ALL subfolders)
# -------------------------------------------------------------------

# 1. Dependency folders in any sub-directory
# This ignores 'node_modules' wherever it is found inside the repo.
**/node_modules/

# 2. Build/Output folders in any sub-directory
# Ignore common build folders like 'dist', 'build', 'out'
**/build/
**/dist/
**/out/

# 3. Development/Local/Cache Files in any sub-directory
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.DS_Store
**/.vscode/

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# SPECIFIC IGNORES (for projects that use unique folders)
# -------------------------------------------------------------------

# Example: If your backend uses a unique 'venv' for Python
**/venv/

# Example: If your frontend uses a specific CRA cache folder
**/npm-debug.log*

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# REPOSITORY ROOT IGNORES (only files/folders directly in /React-Router)
# -------------------------------------------------------------------

# Files directly in the root of the repository
/package-lock.json
/yarn.lock